        <item>
            <title>1.1.2</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 16:52:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Nanako0129/TokenBar/releases/tag/v1.1.2</link>
            <sparkle:version>168</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<b>Improved:</b>
<ul>
<li>Much lower background CPU usage. The log-parsing engine no longer keeps a worker thread spinning for every CPU core, and the popover pauses its polling while it is closed, so TokenBar stops holding a CPU core busy in the background.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
