        <item>
            <title>1.1.1</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 03:49:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>156</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <link>https://github.com/Nanako0129/TokenBar/releases/tag/v1.1.1</link>
            <description><![CDATA[
<b>New:</b>
<ul>
<li>Brand logos for the Cline, jcode, MiMo Code, and gjc tabs, instead of a letter badge.</li>
</ul>
<b>Improved:</b>
<ul>
<li>The client-tab row now scrolls with a plain vertical mouse wheel, so a mouse without a horizontal-scroll wheel can reach every tab.</li>
</ul>
<b>Fixes:</b>
<ul>
<li>Antigravity CLI now shows the shared Antigravity quota instead of an empty or duplicate limit card.</li>
</ul>
      ]]></description>
